Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Code Outline (pseudo-code)", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.755274445590074*^9, 
  3.7552744559729652`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a999db28-361d-461a-aa5d-\
7280f803b010"],

Cell["\<\
1. Define a grid
2. Sample functions on grid
3. Calculate, at each shift position (shift performed with circshift, \
interpolation, or function resampling):
\t3.1 function product
\t3.2 integral of 3.1 (i.e., the convolution)
\t3.3 record the shifted function
4. Visualize the results of 3.1-3.3\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7552892047917*^9, 3.75528930458457*^9}, {
  3.755289365374763*^9, 3.7552893903903217`*^9}, {3.755290236954488*^9, 
